I will never forget winning the 1990 Little Brown Jugette with Newmark Real Estate's Jeff Gural. harnessracing.com/news/main/… I dont have the video but I was in emergency surgery at Mt Sinai Hospital after suffering a near fatal accident driving one of my horses at the Lycoming
County Fair. Never did see the race. Five broken ribs, broken leg and seven broken vertebrae in my back. Drs didnt think I would walk again.... That is truly a horse of a different color!
